{"tid":2170269,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"泰語 交流 學習 討論 集中串","createTime":"2020-08-23T07:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T23:27:32.000Z","uid":354971,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4c91333aa801c7288073bc0ec358807c644796f2","tid":2170269,"uid":354971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:02:02.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>入門需知</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打嘅整理,入門需要嘅工具資訊有齊:<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/%E5%AD%B8%E6%A5%B5%E9%83%BD%E5%94%94%E8%AD%98/thai-4bcf9be38696\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%2594%2594%25E8%25AD%2598%2Fthai-4bcf9be38696&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTLyGpUrO7QrNXIpVIwIXQug%3D&h=5b7a2c48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/%E5%AD%B8%E6%A5%B5%E9%83%BD%E5%94%94%E8%AD%98/thai-4bcf9be38696</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>交流TG</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MBl3wBsirru8NkgzP7IdVg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMBl3wBsirru8NkgzP7IdVg&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTLyGpUrO7QrNXIpVIwIXQug%3D&h=17e5054e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MBl3wBsirru8NkgzP7IdVg</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>基本介紹</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Hea mode/旅行會話 mode: </strong><br />\n恭喜你,可以無視下面嘅廢話<br />\n<br />\n<strong>認真mode:</strong><br />\n泰文同廣東話非常相似,有聲調(5個), 無tense, 有齊p t k m n ng尾音, 文法用起嚟熟口熟面,加上唔少字讀音非常相近。<br />\n<br />\n泰文係一個(相對上)先難後易嘅語言,你喺開始嘅一兩個月會應對以下挑戰:<br />\n背44個個樣好似嘅輔音字母 - 大部分要背<br />\n背21個個樣好似嘅元音字母 - 係,背晒佢<br />\n睇4個聲調符號 - 當你以為睇住聲調符號就知道點讀嘅時候, 唔好意思,泰文聲調係要計算咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />捱過咗呢部分嘅朋友,恭喜你,你宜家已經識讀九成泰文字,歡迎進入泰語的世界"},{"pid":"eed72384190f527b6cfcc71740fb5ef9e4af1499","tid":2170269,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:12:59.000Z","msg":"其實有冇人研究過<br />\n點解泰文發音會令到香港人覺得尷尬o既?<br />\n令香港人覺得似講粗口, 講核突野咁, 冇辦法同優雅連上關係<br />\n<br />\n全世界係淨係香港人對泰文先有呢種感覺?<br />\n定只要以廣東話做母語既人都會有?<br />\n定世界有其他語言地方都對泰文有呢種感覺?"},{"pid":"52f4102ee86939a15c7c0b80c5600a6dcd21c07f","tid":2170269,"uid":354971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eed72384190f527b6cfcc71740fb5ef9e4af1499","tid":2170269,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:12:59.000Z","msg":"其實有冇人研究過<br />\n點解泰文發音會令到香港人覺得尷尬o既?<br />\n令香港人覺得似講粗口, 講核突野咁, 冇辦法同優雅連上關係<br />\n<br />\n全世界係淨係香港人對泰文先有呢種感覺?<br />\n定只要以廣東話做母語既人都會有?<br />\n定世界有其他語言地方都對泰文有呢種感覺?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:36:21.000Z","msg":"我估係因為&ldquo;閪&rdquo;同&ldquo;仔&rdquo;係高頻率使用音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8937ba3ada0c86f80a6a99e99e8aa245acee65","tid":2170269,"uid":48729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eed72384190f527b6cfcc71740fb5ef9e4af1499","tid":2170269,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T07:12:59.000Z","msg":"其實有冇人研究過<br />\n點解泰文發音會令到香港人覺得尷尬o既?<br />\n令香港人覺得似講粗口, 講核突野咁, 冇辦法同優雅連上關係<br />\n<br />\n全世界係淨係香港人對泰文先有呢種感覺?<br />\n定只要以廣東話做母語既人都會有?<br />\n定世界有其他語言地方都對泰文有呢種感覺?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T08:08:58.000Z","msg":"確實係有啲詞好似廣東話粗口。<br />\n好似「等陣」係 <span class=\"green\">เดี๋ยว</span> diao (R<span class=\"small\">ising</span>調)   聽落就好似廣東話嘅「屌」；仲有上面 #疹馬擇康貢 巴打講嘅 <span class=\"red\">ให้</span> hai (F<span class=\"small\">alling</span>調），意思係「畀」、「令到」，聽落就好似廣東話嘅「閪」。<br />\n不過識得咁上下多字，其實講嗰陣完全唔會諗起廣東話。好快就會冇咗呢種感覺。<br />\n仲有其他近音詞可以睇呢度：<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/學極都唔識/98ec148f76ba\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%E5%AD%B8%E6%A5%B5%E9%83%BD%E5%94%94%E8%AD%98%2F98ec148f76ba&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTLyGpUrO7QrNXIpVIwIXQug%3D&h=24ecf485\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/學極都唔識/98ec148f76ba</a>"},{"pid":"8728c078d947d166eea6f4f8ad0b6209a602db